I guess Lady Gaga won in the end, though.

248
00:11:23,735 --> 00:11:27,737
另一则新闻 我有点喜欢这个眼罩
In other news, I kind of like this eye-patch.

249
00:11:27,739 --> 00:11:29,572
我知道你喜欢 你刚刚一直在地铁里
I know you do, you were pretending to be

250
