And by eye doctor, I mean that first-year med student

254
00:11:41,086 --> 00:11:43,636
那个一年级医学生
we gave the free dessert to.

255
00:11:43,638 --> 00:11:45,972
难过的日子只有一只眼能看见
A few days, which is a bummer, 'cause only seeing half

