in this totally awesome suit,

369
00:17:09,464 --> 00:17:12,465
我比较了解被欺负的感受
but I know a little something about being bullied.

370
00:17:12,467 --> 00:17:13,883
当我还是小孩的时候...
As a little child...

371
00:17:13,885 --> 00:17:16,586
